# Mini Challenge 3

## Full CRUD(S) support for Issues

### Acceptance Criteria
1. Users should be able to create new issues.
2. Users should be able to see a detail page for existing issues.
3. Users should be able to update existing issues.
4. Users should be able to delete existing issues (permanent delete).

## Bonus:
Users should be able to "archive" issues (these no longer show up on the board). This is a soft delete.

## Bonus 2:
All users must be logged in to access all views.